                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-190-off1030 t18120916-190-cd1031"></join>, four hats, value 3 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18120916-190-victim1518" type="victimName">
                  Nathaniel 
                  Ruth
               <interp inst="t18120916-190-victim1518" type="surname" value="Ruth"></interp>
